data.description: Back on the market due to no fault of the sellers! Check out this amazing Cape Cod 3 BR/2.5BA home located in the desirable Inverness community! Home boasts a spacious den with fireplace with new laminate flooring, a formal dining room with fresh paint and new laminate flooring, master bedroom downstairs with master bath which has fresh paint and new laminate flooring, and a sunroom which can be used as another living area, office, craft room, etc.  Two additional bedrooms and a full bath are located upstairs.  The backyard is completely fenced and includes a detached storage building.  Upgrades per the seller include: A 2022 Goodman 4-ton HVAC unit with warranty, all new ductwork, new paint downstairs (dining, laundry room, foyer, and master bedroom), new carpet on stairs, new exterior paint on front porch, all new laminate in dining, living room, foyer, and master bath, all new light fixtures downstairs, and upgraded electrical downstairs! Schedule a tour of this beauty today!!  HOME IS NOT LOCATED IN A FLOOD ZONE!
